Autogrill Aims to Expand in India, Asia, Chief Tells Messaggero

-- B y   C h i a r a   R e m o n d i n i
-- 
2011-02-13T10:56:58Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-02-13/autogrill-aims-to-expand-in-india-asia-chief-tells-messaggero.html
  Autogrill SpA  aims to expand in  India  and other Asian countries, Chief Executive Officer
Gianmario Tondato told  il Messaggero .  “We want to grow in international markets, especially
emerging economies,” the newspaper cited the CEO as saying in
an interview. He singled out Malaysia,  Sri Lanka  and  Singapore 
as possible locations, it reported. The company is the world’s
biggest manager of airport and highway restaurants.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Chiara Remondini in Milan at 
 cremondini@bloomberg.net   To contact the editors responsible for this story:
Vidya Root at   vroot@bloomberg.net . 